                                | In: ESANN 2018 - 26th European Symposium on Artificial Neural Networks, Computational Intelligence and Machine Learning, 2018, Bruges.
                            p
                                a(class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" data-toggle="collapse" href="#abstract_4" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="abstract_4")
